title: The Land Owner shall have the option of developing AH, OA and handing them over to the MCGM
clause_text: The Land Owner shall have the option of developing AH, OA and handing them over to the MCGM. However, area earmarked for POS, AH, OA shall be levelled along with construction of compound wall before handing over to MCGM.
